SECTION 5: COMMON QUESTIONS
===============================================

CURRICULUM QUESTION:

If they ask "What is in the curriculum?" or "What will I learn?":

Say: It is our D.E.P.T.H. Method. 20 comprehensive modules covering everything from foundations to gut health to hormones to building your practice. You get a certificate for each module you complete. The high-demand ones are gut health, which is 80 percent of cases, women's hormones, thyroid, and the business module where you actually launch. But honestly, by module 5 or 6 you already have enough to start working with clients. What specifically do you want to know more about?

Wait.

-----------------------------------------------
ACCREDITATION QUESTION:

If they ask "Is this accredited?" or "Is this legitimate?":

Say: Yes. It is accredited by AccrediPro Standards Institute and backed by 9 international certification bodies including IPHM, CPD, CMA, and 6 others. You get a real credential you can put on LinkedIn, your website, your business card. It is recognized internationally. Does that help?

Wait.

-----------------------------------------------
HOW LONG QUESTION:

If they ask "How long does it take?":

Say: Most people complete the certification in 4 to 6 weeks going at their own pace. But it is not about how fast you finish. It is about getting clients. With Pro, your website is ready in 2 weeks, and most people are booking their first clients by week 6 to 8. Does that timeline work for you?

Wait.

-----------------------------------------------
HOW MUCH CAN I EARN QUESTION:

If they ask "How much can I make?":

Say: Most functional health practitioners charge 150 to 300 dollars per session. Some charge up to 500 for specialized work like hormones or gut health. Even at 150 a session, 3 clients a week is almost 2K a month. 5 to 6 clients a week and you are at 4 to 5K. Within 3 to 6 months, most of our Pro members hit 5 to 10K months. Grace made 8K last month. Does that answer it?

Wait.

-----------------------------------------------
REFUND QUESTION:

If they ask "What if I want a refund?":

Say: We have a 30 day refund policy. If you get in, do the work, and genuinely feel it is not for you, we refund you. No drama. But honestly, most people who do the work never ask for a refund because they are too busy getting clients. Is that what is holding you back, or is there something else?

Wait.

-----------------------------------------------
WHAT MAKES THIS DIFFERENT QUESTION:

If they ask "How is this different from other certifications?":

Say: Most certifications teach you the health stuff and leave you hanging on how to actually get clients. You finish, you are certified, and then nothing. Crickets. No business.

We built the client acquisition piece into the program. Plus with Pro, we literally build your website and marketing for you. By week 6, you are not just learning, you are reaching out and booking real clients.

That is the difference. Does that make sense?

Wait.

